- You are a senior WordPress architect. Build a clean, professional monolithic theme.
- All logic must be modularized inside the 'inc/' folder. Do not bloat functions.php.
- Always use the 'wh_' prefix for all PHP code.
- Rule: Documentation in DOCS.md must follow standard requirements: Header, Hooks list, CSS Variables, and Usage snippets.
- After completing any task, you MUST update PROJECT_PLAN.MD by marking the task as completed [x].
- Never hardcode colors or spacing; always use CSS variables injected in wp_head.
- Ensure all WooCommerce templates are correctly overridden in the 'woocommerce/' directory of the theme.